{
  "stem": "11771.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know you want me to help me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I figure I'll go to the rest of the Jews who are in hiding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in case, I wouldn't be able to manage there, I will come back to you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they say, both of them-- [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yusiska, ?] do whatever you wish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our door is open for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whenever you come back, you know how to open the door in the barn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Go in.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Be our guest.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We'll support you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we'll hide you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But if you feel like to go back to the rest of the Jews that are hiding in the forest and the pits, do your wish.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I came back to the Jews [? faced-- ?] who ran away from the Radun Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I met survivors, one of them who hit me in my back-- in my face, he iddn't want to see me here when I ran away from Eishyshok.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I telled-- I told him, [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Froike-- ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Froim ?] was his name-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] did you-- couldn't you foresee that the fate of Radun is going to be the same as Eishyshok?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You made me run away to Yanova.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went through the whole thing now I [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eight months I could live like a human like you did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I didn't-- I mean, I didn't do him anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Before even the massacre in Radun, I hear that some Russian partisans organizing themselves about 15 kilometers from Juzia, where I was sitting.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Radun still remained a Jewish ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I get out-- got out from the barn, I told him, I'm going to look for the partisans from the Russian, in [INAUDIBLE] for a week.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
